    {
      "id": "r015",
      "type": "estimate",
      "topic": "architecture",
      "content": "Minimum viable prototype requires: (1) Node.js HTTP server ~200 LOC, (2) WebSocket push to browser ~100 LOC, (3) Browser UI with approve/deny + activity feed ~300 LOC HTML/JS, (4) Hook config in settings.json ~20 lines. Total: ~600 LOC, zero npm dependencies if using Node built-in http + ws modules.",
